==商业生涯==
宾德拉还是一位商人，拥有[[美国|美国]]科罗拉多大学[[MBA|MBA]]的他<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestatesman.net/page.news.php?clid=5&id=217983|publisher=The Statesman|date=2008-08-11|title=Prodigy who’s fulfilled his early promise|accessdate=2008-08-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040904090653/http://www.thestatesman.net/page.news.php?clid=5|archivedate=2004-09-04}}</ref>是 [https://web.archive.org/web/20080813222039/http://www.abhinavfuturistics.com/ Abhinav Futuristics公司] 的CEO，这家位于[[昌迪加尔|昌迪加尔]]的公司，以销售各种电脑游戏配件为主<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/Abhinav_Bindra_One_of_the_finest_talent_Chandigarh_has_produced/articleshow/3351560.cms |title=Abhinav Bindra: One of the finest talent Chandigarh has produced |accessdate=2008-08-12 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713134230/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/Abhinav_Bindra_One_of_the_finest_talent_Chandigarh_has_produced/articleshow/3351560.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

